name: Dansko "Professional" Pearlized Patent Leather Clog
description:
This just in! Dansko’s bestselling “Professional” clog is now available in a pearlized patent leather upper for an ultra-dressy appearance. An innovative design molds to the foot’s natural contour, providing comfort and relief when standing for long periods of time. The epitome of fashion-forward and functional footwear also features generous padding, a shock-absorbing polyurethane outsole, an antimicrobial sock liner and a footbed that absorbs and evaporates perspiration. 

• Patentleather upper 
• Heel height: 2” 
• Anti-skid tread 
• Stapled polyurethane outsole provides shock absorption and flexibility 
• Instep collar is generously padded 
• Rocker-bottom sole propels the foot forward when walking 
• Antimicrobial leather socklining 
• Durable thermoplastic toe box allows toes to move comfortably while providing toe protection 
• Thermoplastic urethane heel counter acts as a natural shoehorn, provides lateral stability and allows heel to move up and down when walking 
• Breathable polyurethane footbed absorbs and evaporates perspiration 
• Withstands surfaces of extreme heat and cold 
• Design follows the natural contours of the foot 
• Polypropylene inner frame provides stability and reduces torque 
• Dansko’s stapled outsole carries the seal of approval from the American Podiatric Medical Association 
• Dansko’s stapled outsole has been tested by Precision Testing Laboratories in Nashville, Tennessee

This shoe runs true to size. If you are between sizes, we recommend going up to the next full size.

name: Skechers Work “Shape Up” Shoe

Tell your old shoes to ship out – and get the “Shape Up”. Contemporary lace-up leather upper shoe incorporates a revolutionary design that offers a wealth of health-related benefits that work as you work. An OSHA-compliant outsole keeps you on your feet while a shock-absorbent foam midsole provides an exercise-based effect that aims to improve posture, reduce joint stress, burn calories, improve circulation, strengthen the back, reduce cellulite and tone and tighten various muscles. Additional benefits include a supportive polyurethane frame, a cushiony insole and a fabric lining. Each pair of shoes comes with a detailed exercise guide. 

• Lace-up shoe 
• Leather upper 
• OSHA-compliant slip-resistant rubber outsole 
• Firm polyurethane frame supports and stabilizes the foot 
• Kinetic wedge super soft foam midsole is designed to absorb shock and provide an exercising effect 
• Cushioned insole 
• Padded collar and tongue 
• Fabric shoe lining 
• Stitching detail 
• Sole rated ASTM F 1677-96 Mark II 
• Heel height: 1 ½” midsole height at center 
• Comes with a detailed exercise guide 
• Designed to: tone muscles, improve posture, reduce joint stress, burn calories, improve blood circulation, tighten abdominal muscles, strengthen the back, firm buttocks muscles, reduce cellulite, tone thighs, firm calf muscles 
• Please Note: running in “Shape Up” is not recommended 

This shoe runs true to size. If you are between sizes, we recommend going up to the next full size.

Portable, practical and reliable, this battery-operated fingertip pulse oximeter is the non-invasive solution for measuring the oxygen saturation of patient’s blood (SPO2) in order to assess the need for additional oxygen. Battery-operated, it also includes a rubberized bumper to prevent scrapes and nicks and a lanyard for convenient carrying. Perfect for visiting nurses, home use, EMS and more.

• Carry lanyard and rubberized bumper included 
• Battery operated

Measuring 6 yards, they’re extremely portable, allowing for easy access to exercise at work, home or while traveling. Perfect for physical therapists, patients recovering from shoulder or knee surgery, daily exercise routines or birthing, pilates or yoga classes.
